{"tid":2055132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控主席據報警告英國若禁用華為或招中國報復","createTime":"2020-06-07T17:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T19:36:40.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b5056c550c6210648d2f8756ffc8474e630354a3","tid":2055132,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530725-20200608.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530725-20200608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3722a918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530725-20200608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=38c7bf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530725-20200608.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》引述消息人士報道，匯控主席杜嘉祺曾經向英國首相約翰遜的顧問表示，如果英國政府禁止中國電訊設備商華為參與5G網絡建設，匯豐可能會遭到中國政府報復。首相府及滙豐發言人都拒絕評論報道內容。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府早前容許華為參與5G網絡建設的非核心部分，但上月有報道指，英國計劃改變主意，完全排除華為在5G網絡建設之外。"},{"pid":"61176881fee186b9dd1fd6894d3b2a688a916a32","tid":2055132,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好做中國生意囉"},{"pid":"5492d6425b7569e3b05eb2864af6bcd445b4d78e","tid":2055132,"uid":72819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61176881fee186b9dd1fd6894d3b2a688a916a32","tid":2055132,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好做中國生意囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"中國+香港盈利貢獻好似大過100%...<br />\n(即係歐美業務長期蝕錢要亞洲賺錢黎冚)"},{"pid":"8537367876c9743fd9028a39723302613d1bfbae","tid":2055132,"uid":277702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5492d6425b7569e3b05eb2864af6bcd445b4d78e","tid":2055132,"uid":72819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61176881fee186b9dd1fd6894d3b2a688a916a32","